text: Kingsley Eduwo (born 19 June 1996) is a Nigerian international footballer who plays for CS Sfaxien as a striker. ==Career== Born in Lagos, Eduwo has played club football for Gateway United, Sunshine Stars, Lobi Stars, CS Sfaxien and Al-Najaf.
